Invite User B as a member. 5. Switch to User B's account. 6. Open the same workspace chat. 7. Switch back to User A's account. 8. Create an empty report. 9. Switch again to User B´s account. 10. Right-click on the placeholder and tap "Copy message" 11. Paste the message on the composer 12. Verify that the copied message is the report title. 13. Open report and return to workspace chat. 14.
